 </code><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code>Amends the State Employees Group Insurance Act of 1971, the Illinois </code><code>Public Aid Code, the Problem Pregnancy Health Services and Care Act, and </code><code>the Illinois Abortion Law of 1975. Restores the provisions that were </code><code>amended by Public Act 100-538 to the form in which they existed before </code><code>their amendment by Public Act 100-538.</code><code>
